  "description": "As if Salvador Dali and Willie Nelson made a musical COMEDY. “Mark Twain on acid”- Artistry Mag 20X BEST OF FEST Winners (Tales Too Tall for Trailers ★★★★★ Edm Sun / Away, Now ★★★★★ - Free Press) Paul Strickland &amp; Erika MacDonald’s one-man show, interrupted by a hilarious guest. Don't miss this surreal SONG-FILLED LAUGH FEST!",
